{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't finish to explain to him that only those kind of people could work, because the ones who were very obvious, you couldn't-- you couldn't use them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he went, by bicycle, 200 kilometers to come and tell me that he had heard that my husband had been wounded.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I said immediately, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where is he?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, no, you're not going because it's completely in German territory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If he's wounded, if he's in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He kept saying to me-- the whole day long, he kept telling me I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finally, at night, he had to tell me the truth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had been killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I-- it was-- it was absolutely-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always felt he-- he escaped so many times for four years-- I mean, there were so many-- they were after him so many times that I didn't think it could happen again.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just didn't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, it did happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it happened in a very, very dramatic way because he took his whole team of men and their-- their order was to stop a train that was leaving, through Switzerland, to go back to Germany with all the files of the Resistance-- with all the files of the people who were-- that they had been able to snitch out.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the order west to stop that train at a certain spot in the-- in a mountain-- in the valley down below the railroad track, where then they were up in the mountain, themselves.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
